article.description: — Alex Morales had 21 points as Wagner extended its winning streak to 14 games, topping Mount St. Mary's 69-57 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Morales carries Wagner over Mount St. Mary's 69-57
article.linkText: Morales carries Wagner over Mount St. Mary's 69-57
article.story: NEW YORK -- — Alex Morales had 21 points as Wagner extended its winning streak to 14 games, topping Mount St. Mary's 69-57 on Thursday night. Will Martinez had 13 points for Wagner (17-2, 11-0 Northeast Conference). Raekwon Rogers added 10 rebounds. Jalen Benjamin had 16 points for the Mountaineers (11-12, 7-4).
